    {{#> case/paragraphe title="The challenge" }}
        <p>15% of H&M online customers are not members of the loyalty program.
            How might we encourage them to sign up?</p>
    {{/case/paragraphe}}

    {{#> case/paragraphe title="My role" }}
        <p><strong>Product Designer</strong> in a Team in charge of increasing the number of sign ups. The team hadn't
            had a Product Designer before.
        </p>
    {{/case/paragraphe}}

    {{#> case/paragraphe title="The process" }}
        <p>When I joined, the team was bombarded with requests to add more features, or put the sign up button
            in more places. But there was little data to back that up! So, I conducted research
            to help us decide what to prioritise.</p>

    {{/case/paragraphe}}

    {{#> case/twoColumn }}
        {{#> case/leftColumn title="Research" img="img/hm1_signup_Clicktale.png" alt="21% drop out at the date of birth. Drop out is much lower for other fields (3 to 4%)" }}
